title: Galadhrim Elves At War: Dwarves Attack! - Total War: Rise of Mordor Mod Gameplay
description:
Galadhrim Elves At War: Dwarves Attack! - Total War: Rise of Mordor Mod Gameplay - Today we are looking at a submod for Rise of Mordor.  The Galadhrim Elves are now playable for Total War: Attila.  We will see them in action in today's siege battle.  Jackie fish will be attacking me as the dwarves.  And we will see the feud between Dwarves and Elves come to a head.  This is a pretty cool chill battle just showing off the new elves!  Enjoy the Siege battle :D

Elves Mod: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=902039224

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
